title: Eps. 93 - Love Conquers
description:
The guys are back from a fun filled week active week and the topic is LOVE. Specifically Love Conquers, which is the latest viral video from ET. After the tragic event in Las Vegas ET gave a powerful speech during his weekly Success Series event. On the podcast ET talks about what it feels like to deliver a powerful speech such as that one and he speaks about how and why you should practice love. The guys also transition into talking about the importance of going through a tough season and how it shapes you. Grab a friend or family member who may be going through a tough time to listen to this episode. If you haven’t seen the Love Conquers video yet do so now.
 Love Conquers
